https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Audio-visual_speech_recognition
Now imagine creating a virtual video of what's happening on the other side of the phone only from audio.
The 3D image wouldn't be as real but it would try to creat the environment details.
At first the AI would recognise the received sounds, like other people around the interlocutor, cars passing by, doors opening ...
An approximate image representation is created and transmitted to the user visual.
